      <title>博客搭建: 使用安知鱼主题美化你的博客</title>
      <link href="/posts/c7ff2af7/"/>
      <url>/posts/c7ff2af7/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本教程参考内容 <a href="https://docs.anheyu.com/">安知鱼主题文档</a></p><p>封面来源 <a href="https://docs.anheyu.com/">安知鱼主题文档</a></p><h1 id="主题安装"><a href="#主题安装" class="headerlink" title="主题安装"></a>主题安装</h1><p>Tips: 如果你发现安装速度太慢或无法安装 请切换网络</p><p>在你博客目录下打开终端 输入以下内容安装主题</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> -b main https://github.com/anzhiyu-c/hexo-theme-anzhiyu.git themes/anzhiyu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着输入以下内容安装渲染器</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果你是Linux用户或mac用户 在你博客目录下打开终端 输入以下内容进行覆盖配置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cp</span> -rf ./themes/anzhiyu/_config.yml ./_config.anzhiyu.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果你是Windows用户 请自行复制&#x2F;themes&#x2F;anzhiyu&#x2F;_config.yml此文件到你博客目录 并重命名为_config.anzhiyu.yml 进行覆盖配置</p><p>修改你博客目录下的_config.yml文件 找到theme 修改主题为anzhiyu</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">anzhiyu</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来 你就可以进行本地预览了 输入以下内容本地预览 以确保主题正确安装</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="生成标签页和分类页"><a href="#生成标签页和分类页" class="headerlink" title="生成标签页和分类页"></a>生成标签页和分类页</h1><p>1.在你博客目录下打开终端 输入以下内容生成标签页</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到 你的博客目录&#x2F;source&#x2F;tags&#x2F;index.md这个文件 修改为以下内容 时间自行替换</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 标签</span><br><span class="line">date: 2025-08-09 12:15:49</span><br><span class="line">aside: false</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">comments: false</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">top<span class="emphasis">_img: false</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section">---</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.在你博客目录下打开终端 输入以下内容生成分类页</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到 你的博客目录&#x2F;source&#x2F;categories&#x2F;index.md这个文件 修改为以下内容 时间自行替换</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2025-08-09 12:15:49</span><br><span class="line">aside: false</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">comments: false</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">top<span class="emphasis">_img: false</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section">---</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="其它功能配置-可选"><a href="#其它功能配置-可选" class="headerlink" title="其它功能配置(可选)"></a>其它功能配置(可选)</h1><p>1.安装abbrlink插件(随机你文章的链接)</p><p>在你博客目录下打开终端输入以下内容</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后打开你博客目录下的_config.yml(不是_config.anzhiyu.yml)文件 找到permalink 修改为以下内容</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">posts/:abbrlink</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还是这个文件 到末尾处(或随便一个空白处)添加以下内容</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># abbrlink config</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">abbrlink:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">alg:</span> <span class="string">crc32</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rep:</span> <span class="string">hex</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.安装文章置顶插件</p><p>在你博客目录下打开终端输入以下内容</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-topindex --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到你要设置置顶的文章 添加top参数 以下为示例</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">----</span><br><span class="line">title: 文章标题</span><br><span class="line">date: 文章创建时间</span><br><span class="line">top: 1</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 分类</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">- 标签</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">----</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果有多个文章要设置置顶 修改top后面的数字 数字越大 权重越高</p><p>更多关于安知鱼主题的美化和功能请自行访问 <a href="https://docs.anheyu.com/">安知鱼主题文档</a> 感谢你的观看</p>]]></content>
      
      
